text: Hi Zulakha, good to connect with you. I started work as a nurse and made a transition into management after 11 years working clinically. I continue my clinical work to date as I enjoy this immensely. I worked my way through management routes becoming an executive director role today.
I wish you well on your journey; my advice is - have self belief as you can achieve what you want if you're willing to work at it
Hoping your A levels go well and feel free to keep open dialogue. Best wishes, David
